<h2>Data Description</h2>

<p>This repository contains financial statement data for various companies sourced from 
<a href="https://cafef.vn" target="_blank">cafef.vn</a>. The data includes three types of financial statements:</p>

<ul>
    <li><strong>BS (Balance Sheet):</strong> Provides an overview of a company's assets, liabilities, and shareholder equity at a specific point in time.</li>
    <li><strong>CF (Cash Flow Statement):</strong> Shows the cash inflows and outflows from the company's operating, investing, and financing activities.</li>
    <li><strong>IS (Income Statement):</strong> Details the company's revenue, expenses, and profits over a specific period.</li>
</ul>

<p>The data is organized by company and year, and can be used for financial analysis, modeling, or comparison between companies.</p>
